Class AntHill

  • java.lang.Object
    • ants.AntGameObject
      • ants.AntHill
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<AntHill>

    public class AntHill
extends AntGameObject
implements java.lang.Comparable<AntHill>
    This class represents an ant hill where ants can spawn from. A hill belongs to a bot.
    Author:
    Benjamin
